    "Title": "Una plataforma para el desarrollo sostenible del país",
    "Published Date": "2022-10-10T19:21:38Z",
    "Cover Image": "wix:image://v1/18da1d_3ccdfdf248ff4b25a6fb24fa3c970525~mv2.png/18da1d_3ccdfdf248ff4b25a6fb24fa3c970525~mv2.png#originWidth=1748&originHeight=1240",
