    "Title": "Una cooperativa es una forma de no estar solo\": entrevista a Alexandre Roig, presidente del INAES",
    "Published Date": "2021-06-15T08:12:02Z",
    "Cover Image": "wix:image://v1/02084a_b1a0cd0732ea4a35b2b9e3b8292e0af5~mv2.jpg/02084a_b1a0cd0732ea4a35b2b9e3b8292e0af5~mv2.jpg#originWidth=1000&originHeight=1000",
