    "Title": "Para una educación equitativa es urgente resolver la brecha digital\": entrevista a Melina Furman",
    "Published Date": "2021-03-09T03:00:00Z",
    "Cover Image": "wix:image://v1/6e843c_25bca036eea4415e90e15ea64d7aa612~mv2.jpg/6e843c_25bca036eea4415e90e15ea64d7aa612~mv2.jpg#originWidth=1004&originHeight=565",
